item.title: You Are Chosen—Worthy, Loved, & Accepted | Chosen By Jesus with Kelley Tyan & Taylor Tyan
item.description: Have you ever felt overlooked or like you didn’t belong? In this powerful episode of Chosen By Jesus, Kelley and Taylor Tyan remind you of this life-changing truth: You are chosen—not because of what you’ve done, but because of who God is....
